                        Protection of Civilians in Current Conflicts – Operational Challenges and Priorities
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[23.09.2010]</p>
                <p>- In a broader perspective, the focus of our work must always be on the consequences felt on the ground, says Minister of Defence Grete Faremo.</p>
                
                
