            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fd/whats-new/News/2010/Important-cooperation-agreement-between-Norway-and-Poland.html?id=613940" title="">
                        Important cooperation agreement between Norway and Poland
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[10.09.2010]</p>
                <p>On 7 September 2010 the Norwegian Ministry of Defence entered into an agreement with the Polish Ministry of Defence concerning increased cooperation on defence equipment.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                <span id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_listingUniversal_lstUniversal_ctl03_Label1"></span>                 
           </div>
